svg.script: var dots = document.querySelectorAll('.dot'),tl = new TimelineMax({repeat: -1}); function getDotsWaveTl(){var dotsWaveTl = new TimelineMax();[].forEach.call(dots, function(element, index){var dotWaveTl = new TimelineMax(),delay = 0.15;dotWaveTl.to(element, 0.4, {y: -7, ease:Power1.easeOut}).to(element, 0.8, {y: 7, ease:Power1.easeInOut}).to(element, 0.4, {y: 0, ease:Power1.easeIn});dotsWaveTl.add(dotWaveTl, delay*index);});return dotsWaveTl;}tl.add(getDotsWaveTl());
